  <h2>Blog</h2>

  <p>
    I occasionally write blog posts about software engineering and technology.
  </p>

  <SectionHobbies />

  <SectionQA />

  <h2>Contact</h2>

  <p>
    If you'd like to get in touch, feel free to reach out on GitHub or LinkedIn.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
